<item>
            <title>[LU-8339] Lock improvement for kiblnd_check_sends</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-8339</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;kiblnd_check_sends() takes conn::ibc_lock at the beginning and releases this lock at the end. This is inefficient because most use-cases needs to release ibc_lock before caling this function.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Change this function to kiblnd_check_sends_locked() and avoid unnecessary lock dances.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
